<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>✈️ Material de Apoio — Piloto Privado ANAC</title>
  <style>
    /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --azul:      #1a3a5c;
      --azul2:     #2563eb;
      --azul3:     #dbeafe;
      --verde:     #166534;
      --verde2:    #16a34a;
      --verde3:    #dcfce7;
      --laranja:   #92400e;
      --laranja2:  #d97706;
      --laranja3:  #fef3c7;
      --vermelho:  #991b1b;
      --vermelho2: #dc2626;
      --vermelho3: #fee2e2;
      --amarelo:   #78350f;
      --amarelo2:  #f59e0b;
      --amarelo3:  #fffbeb;
      --cinza:     #1f2937;
      --cinza2:    #6b7280;
      --cinza3:    #f3f4f6;
      --branco:    #ffffff;
      --sombra:    0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      --radius:    12px;
      --radius2:   8px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f0f4f8;
      color: var(--cinza);
      line-height: 1.7;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
    #sidebar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 260px;
      height: 100vh;
      background: var(--azul);
      overflow-y: auto;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 0 0 40px 0;
      box-shadow: 4px 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    #sidebar .logo {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2540, #2563eb);
      padding: 28px 20px 20px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    #sidebar .logo .plane { font-size: 2.8rem; }
    #sidebar .logo h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 6px; }
    #sidebar .logo p  { color: #93c5fd; font-size: 0.78rem; margin-top: 4px; }

    #sidebar nav { padding: 16px 0; }

    #sidebar nav .nav-section {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #93c5fd;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 16px 20px 6px 20px;
    }

    #sidebar nav a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-left: 3px solid transparent;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    #sidebar nav a:hover,
    #sidebar nav a.active {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      color: #fff;
      border-left-color: #60a5fa;
    }

    #sidebar nav a .icon { font-size: 1.1rem; min-width: 22px; text-align: center; }

    /* ===== TOGGLE MOBILE ===== */
    #menuToggle {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      top: 14px; left: 14px;
      z-index: 200;
      background: var(--azul2);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
    }

    /* ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== */
    #main {
      margin-left: 260px;
      padding: 40px 40px 60px 40px;
      max-width: 1100px;
    }

    /* ===== SEÇÕES ===== */
    .section { margin-bottom: 60px; }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a5c 0%, #2563eb 60%, #0ea5e9 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 48px 40px;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '✈';
      position: absolute;
      right: 30px; top: 20px;
      font-size: 8rem;
      opacity: 0.10;
    }

    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .hero p  { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #bfdbfe; margin-top: 10px; max-width: 600px; }

    .hero .badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 20px; }
    .hero .badge {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ===== CARD GRIDS ===== */
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .card-grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    /* ===== CARD BASE ===== */
    .card {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 24px;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.14); }

    /* ===== PROVA INFO CARDS ===== */
    .info-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .info-card {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 20px 16px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 4px solid var(--azul2);
    }

    .info-card .num { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--azul2); }
    .info-card .lbl { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--cinza2); margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }

    /* ===== ALERTA ===== */
    .alerta {
      background: var(--vermelho3);
      border-left: 5px solid var(--vermelho2);
      border-radius: var(--radius2);
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--vermelho);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    /* ===== DISCIPLINA TABS ===== */
    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .tab-btn {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #e2e8f0;
      color: var(--cinza2);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .tab-btn:hover { background: var(--azul3); color: var(--azul); }
    .tab-btn.active { background: var(--azul2); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.3); }

    .tab-content { display: none; }
    .tab-content.active { display: block; }

    /* ===== DISCIPLINA HEADER ===== */
    .disc-header {
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px 32px;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
    }

    .disc-header h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 900; }
    .disc-header p  { opacity: 0.88; margin-top: 6px; font-size: 0.97rem; }

    .disc-tv  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a5c, #2563eb); }
    .disc-ct  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c2d12, #ea580c); }
    .disc-reg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14532d, #16a34a); }
    .disc-met { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #78350f, #d97706); }
    .disc-nav { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7f1d1d, #dc2626); }

    /* ===== CONTEÚDO DA DISCIPLINA ===== */
    .disc-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) { .disc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    /* ===== BOXES ===== */
    .box {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .box h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    /* ===== ASCII / PRÉ-FORMATADO ===== */
    pre {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: var(--radius2);
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-family: 'Courier New', Consolas, monospace;
      margin: 0;
      white-space: pre;
    }

    /* ===== TÓPICOS LIST ===== */
    .topicos-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .topicos-list li {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      color: var(--cinza);
      padding: 5px 8px;
      background: var(--cinza3);
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .topicos-list li::before { content: '▸'; color: var(--azul2); font-weight: 900; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* ===== TEMAS MAIS COBRADOS ===== */
    .temas-list li {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      background: var(--cinza3);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .temas-list li:hover { background: var(--azul3); }
    .temas-list li::before { content: '✅'; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* ===== MNEMÔNICOS ===== */
    .mnemo-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffbeb, #fef3c7);
      border: 2px solid var(--amarelo2);
      border-radius: var(--radius2);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .mnemo-card .code { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--amarelo); letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .mnemo-card .desc { font-size: 0.86rem; color: #78350f; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ===== VÍDEOS ===== */
    .video-card {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius2);
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .video-card:hover { background: var(--azul3); border-color: var(--azul2); transform: translateX(4px); }

    .video-card .thumb {
      width: 52px; height: 52px;
      background: var(--vermelho2);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .video-card .info .titulo { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cinza); }
    .video-card .info .canal  { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--cinza2); margin-top: 3px; }
    .video-card .info .nivel  { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--azul2); font-weight: 700; margin-top: 3px; }

    /* ===== DOWNLOADS ===== */
    .download-card {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 20px 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border-left: 5px solid var(--azul2);
    }

    .download-card:hover { transform: translateX(4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.13); }

    .download-card .dl-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      background: var(--azul3);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .download-card .dl-info { flex: 1; }
    .download-card .dl-info h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--azul); }
    .download-card .dl-info p  { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--cinza2); margin-top: 4px; }
    .download-card .dl-info .importancia { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 6px; }

    .download-card .btn-dl {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: var(--azul2);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      align-self: center;
    }

    .download-card .btn-dl:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .download-card.essencial { border-left-color: #16a34a; }
    .download-card.essencial .dl-icon { background: var(--verde3); }
    .download-card.essencial .btn-dl { background: var(--verde2); }
    .download-card.essencial .btn-dl:hover { background: #15803d; }

    /* ===== CANAIS ===== */
    .canal-card {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 22px;
      border-top: 4px solid var(--vermelho2);
    }

    .canal-card .canal-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .canal-card .canal-logo {
      width: 44px; height: 44px;
      background: var(--vermelho2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: #fff; font-size: 1.3rem; flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .canal-card h3 { font-size: 0.97rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--cinza); }
    .canal-card .foco { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--cinza2); margin-top: 2px; }
    .canal-card .destaque { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--cinza); margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 8px 10px; background: var(--cinza3); border-radius: 6px; }
    .canal-card .avaliacao { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amarelo); margin-bottom: 10px; }

    .btn-canal {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: var(--vermelho2);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-canal:hover { background: #b91c1c; }

    /* ===== PLANO DE ESTUDOS ===== */
    .plano-semana {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      border-left: 5px solid var(--azul2);
    }

    .plano-semana h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--azul); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .plano-semana .ativs { margin-top: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
    .plano-semana .ativ { font-size: 0.86rem; padding: 5px 10px; background: var(--cinza3); border-radius: 5px; display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .plano-semana .ativ::before { content: '→'; color: var(--azul2); font-weight: 900; }
    .plano-semana .meta { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.83rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--verde2); background: var(--verde3); padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-flex; gap: 6px; }

    /* ===== MNEMÔNICOS GERAIS ===== */
    .mnemo-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    /* ===== CHECKLIST ===== */
    .checklist-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius2);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .checklist-item:hover { border-color: var(--azul2); background: var(--azul3); }
    .checklist-item.done { background: var(--verde3); border-color: var(--verde2); }
    .checklist-item.done .cl-text { text-decoration: line-through; color: var(--cinza2); }

    .checklist-item input[type="checkbox"] { width: 18px; height: 18px; cursor: pointer; accent-color: var(--verde2); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
    .checklist-item .cl-text { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; }

    .cl-progress { background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 20px; height: 10px; margin: 16px 0 6px 0; overflow: hidden; }
    .cl-progress-bar { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--verde2), #4ade80); border-radius: 20px; transition: width 0.4s; }
    .cl-count { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--cinza2); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; }

    /* ===== HEADING SEÇÕES ===== */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--azul);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .section-sub {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--cinza2);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .divider { height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--azul2), transparent); border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 28px; }

    /* ===== ILUSTRAÇÃO FULLWIDTH ===== */
    .ilust-full {
      background: var(--branco);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .ilust-full h4 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      color: var(--cinza2);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    /* ===== RESPONSIVO ===== */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      #sidebar { transform: translateX(-100%); }
      #sidebar.open { transform: translateX(0); }
      #main { margin-left: 0; padding: 70px 16px 40px 16px; }
      #menuToggle { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
      .topicos-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero { padding: 32px 20px; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .card-grid, .info-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- BOTÃO MOBILE -->
<button id="menuToggle" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</button>

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<nav id="sidebar">
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="plane">✈️</div>
    <h1>AeroStudy</h1>
    <p>Piloto Privado — ANAC</p>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-section">📋 Início</div>
    <a href="#inicio" class="active"><span class="icon">🏠</span> Início</a>
    <a href="#prova"><span class="icon">📝</span> A Prova</a>
    <a href="#downloads"><span class="icon">📥</span> Downloads Oficiais</a>
    <a href="#canais"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Canais YouTube</a>

    <div class="nav-section">📚 Disciplinas</div>
    <a href="#disciplinas" onclick="showTab('tv')"><span class="icon">🔵</span> Teoria de Voo</a>
    <a href="#disciplinas" onclick="showTab('ct')"><span class="icon">🟠</span> Conhec. Técnicos</a>
    <a href="#disciplinas" onclick="showTab('reg')"><span class="icon">🟢</span> Regulamentos</a>
    <a href="#disciplinas" onclick="showTab('met')"><span class="icon">🟡</span> Meteorologia</a>
    <a href="#disciplinas" onclick="showTab('nav')"><span class="icon">🔴</span> Navegação Aérea</a>

    <div class="nav-section">🗓️ Estudo</div>
    <a href="#mnemonicos"><span class="icon">🧠</span> Mnemônicos</a>
    <a href="#plano"><span class="icon">📅</span> Plano 8 Semanas</a>
    <a href="#checklist"><span class="icon">✅</span> Checklist Final</a>
  </nav>
</nav>

<!-- OVERLAY MOBILE -->
<div id="overlay" onclick="toggleMenu()" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);z-index:99;"></div>

<!-- CONTEÚDO PRINCIPAL -->
<main id="main">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <div class="hero" id="inicio">
    <h1>✈️ Material de Apoio Completo<br>Piloto Privado — ANAC</h1>
    <p>Guia definitivo para aprovação na prova teórica da ANAC. Conteúdo, ilustrações, vídeos e downloads — tudo em um lugar.</p>
    <div class="badges">
      <span class="badge">📋 5 Disciplinas</span>
      <span class="badge">100 Questões</span>
      <span class="badge">70% por disciplina</span>
      <span class="badge">📥 10 Downloads Oficiais</span>
      <span class="badge">🎬 Vídeos Verificados</span>
      <span class="badge">✅ Checklist Interativo</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== A PROVA ===== -->
  <section class="section" id="prova">
    <h2 class="section-title">📝 A Prova Teórica</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Tudo que você precisa saber antes de começar a estudar.</p>
    <div class="divider"></div>

